events.title: FBI Email Transmission of Phone Records
events.description: An FBI email is sent transmitting batch searches of phone toll records, with attachments of data files.

keyFacts: The document is an FBI email dated April 11, 2019, concerning phone toll record searches.
Attachments include batch search data files (347.Asx, 917.Asx, 929 .4sx) related to phone records.
The AT&T records referenced in the email contain two phone numbers.
